WorkItem.Description:
I have tried to access the documentation on two different Machines with Windows 7 64bit.
I can open the file, the Contents/Index side looks correct, but I always see "Navigation to the webpage was canceled" in the main tab.
Could you please check this or let me know if you need further information.

Comments.Message:
Try enabling CHM viewing http://blog.crowe.co.nz/archive/2007/04/13/719.aspx 
Starting with Windows Vista CHM files were blocked by default.
Ok - thanks for the quick answer!
